flowchart TD
  User[Atlas Advisory Group User Prompt]
  Auth[AuthN/AuthZ Resolution\nauth/users.py + permissions.py]
  Query[Query/Chat Request Build]
  ACL[ACL Filter Application\napply_document_access_filter]
  Index[Index Retrieval/Search]
  Citations[Citation Processing]
  Tools[Tool Calls / MCP Calls]
  Response[Grounded Response Returned]
  Logs[Logs + Trace + Metrics]

  User --> Query
  Query --> Auth
  Auth -->|allow| ACL
  Auth -->|deny| Response
  ACL --> Index
  Index --> Citations
  Citations --> Response
  Query --> Tools
  Tools --> Response
  Query --> Logs
  Tools --> Logs
  Auth --> Logs

  U1[Unknown: ingestion-to-index ACL consistency]
  U2[Partially Confirmed: citation completeness for all tool flows]
  Index -.-> U1
  Citations -.-> U2
